isParticle.description: Do you want to enable particle (sprite animation)? Dependents on Sprite.js

isAnimated.description: Do you want to animate the bar fill?

animationDuration.description: Duration of the animation. Default is 1.

isFillColorChange.description: Do you want to enable bar color change, based on its fill status?

lowFillColor.description: Set a color for low levels of bar, 0 to 0.33 local scale

midFillColor.description: Set a color for mid levels of bar, 0.33 to 0.66 local scale

highFillColor.description: Set a color for high levels of bar, 0.66 to 1 local scale

delay.description: Duration of the delay to call "show tooltip" action. Default is 0.6.

motionThreshold.title: Motion Threshold
motionThreshold.description: Number of meters moved in one frame before CCD is enabled

sweptSphereRadius.title: Swept Sphere Radius
sweptSphereRadius.description: This should be below the half extent of the collision volume. E.g For an object of dimensions 1 meter, try 0.2

orbitSensitivity.title: Orbit Sensitivity
orbitSensitivity.description: How fast the camera moves around the orbit. Higher is faster

distanceSensitivity.title: Distance Sensitivity
distanceSensitivity.description: How fast the camera moves in and out. Higher is faster

schema.name: name
schema.description: name is key to trigger specific action
